### Create Artist (PENDING by default)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/artists
Content-Type: application/json
# Authorization: Bearer {{TOKEN}}

{
  "artist_name": "New Artist",
  "biography": "Some biography text",
  "formation_year": 2010,
  "country_code": "US"
}

### Get Artist By Id
GET http://localhost:3000/api/artists/1

### Search Artists (all)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/artists

### Search Artists (filters name contains 'new')
GET http://localhost:3000/api/artists?name=new

### Search Artists (filters by country and status)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/artists?country=US&status=PENDING

### Update Artist (cannot change status directly)
PUT http://localhost:3000/api/artists/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "biography": "Updated bio",
  "formation_year": 2012
}

### Logical Delete Artist (status -> DELETED)
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/artists/1

### Accept Artist (PENDING -> ACTIVE)
PUT http://localhost:3000/api/artists/1/accept

### Reject Artist (PENDING -> REJECTED)
PUT http://localhost:3000/api/artists/1/reject
